column1: 10/7/2024 11:06:56,Yes,Storytelling through Video Games,Remy,Alexia ,Alexia_C_Remy@mcpsmd.org,"Arts, Games/Sports, Music, STEM",Cole Keen,176095@mcpsmd.net,Alex Shachar ,170706@mcpsmd.net,Aman Kalsi, 175563@mcpsmd.net,Arianna Yepes,242717@mcpsmd.net,Thu,Lunch,,Weekly,194,"“Storytelling through Video Games Club” is a club who wants to bring light to the beautiful stories in video games. In everyday life these stories are really overlooked. This occurs because video games have a very bad connotation against them unlike movies or books. When people think of video games, they usually think of games like Call of Duty, Fortnite, Five nights at Freddy’s, etc. So people gloss over them and don’t them a shot. But, also a lot of video games these days are the problem too. I say this because nowadays it’s really hard to pick up a video game without ever playing one before, because you have to learn all the mechanics. Which in the end also deters people from picking up video games as a medium of storytelling. This club wants to change that and to show to people that this medium of storytelling is one of the best. ",https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1qrbmGLaj3D0kyhg_jY_h4Mlg8y0CruiaRqetnrZMJws/edit#slide=id.g30739580f94_0_0,,False,False,False,,"

column3: class=""desc"" colspan=""3"">“Storytelling through Video Games Club” is a club who wants to bring light to the beautiful stories in video games. In everyday life these stories are really overlooked. This occurs because video games have a very bad connotation against them unlike movies or books. When people think of video games, they usually think of games like Call of Duty, Fortnite, Five nights at Freddy’s, etc. So people gloss over them and don’t them a shot. But, also a lot of video games these days are the problem too. I say this because nowadays it’s really hard to pick up a video game without ever playing one before, because you have to learn all the mechanics. Which in the end also deters people from picking up video games as a medium of storytelling. This club wants to change that and to show to people that this medium of storytelling is one of the best.

When people think of video games, they usually think of games like Call of Duty, Fortnite, Five nights at Freddy’s, etc. So people gloss over them and don’t them a shot. But, also a lot of video games these days are the problem too. I say this because nowadays it’s really hard to pick up a video game without ever playing one before, because you have to learn all the mechanics. Which in the end also deters people from picking up video games as a medium of storytelling. This club wants to change that and to show to people that this medium of storytelling is one of the best. column3: class=""desc"" colspan=""3"">The goal of this club is to create a Ski Club that resembles that of North Bethesda Middle School. If you are unfamiliar with the club, during the months of January and start February we hope to be able to have busses on Friday's take all the students that sign up around Thanksgiving to a ski resort such as Whitetail or Liberty. We would then Ski from around 4:30 pm to 9:30 pm, and then arrive back at the school at around 11:00 pm. This club is not meant to be competitive skiing, but instead a fun option for everybody.
